<div class="txtlevel"><p>Proiect de testare pentru studentii din grupa 232.</p></div>
 <br/><a name='toc_1'></a>
<h1 class='doclevel'>1.Test Suite : cmir3500_BBT</h1>
<div><p>Se testeaza adaugarea unui produs nou.</p>
</div><a name="toc_tc29151"></a><p>&nbsp;</p><div> <table class="tc" width="90%" ><tr><th colspan="4">Test Case P232-17: AddProduct_ECP_Valid&nbsp;<span style="font-size: 80%;">[Version  : 1]</span></th></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Author:</span></td><td colspan="3">cmir3500</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan="4"><span class="label">Summary:</span><br /><p>Testarea adaugarii unui produs folosind o valoare din clasa de echivalenta valida pentru pret. Se introduc datele: id=1, nume=&quot;cola&quot;, pret=10. Rezultatul asteptat este ca produsul sa fie salvat cu succes in repository, fara a arunca vreo exceptie.</p>
</td></tr><tr><td colspan="4"><span class="label">Preconditions:</span><br /><p>Aplicatia este pornita si initializata. Nu exista deja un produs salvat cu id-ul 1.</p>
</td></tr><tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Execution type:</span></td><td colspan="3">Automated</td></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Estimated exec. duration (min):</span></td><td colspan="3"></td></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Importance:</span></td><td colspan="3">Medium</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan="4"></td></tr><tr><td > name of the autotest class:</td><td  colspan = "3" >drinkshop.tests.ProductServiceTest</td></tr>
<tr><td > name of the test method:</td><td  colspan = "3" >drinkshop.tests.ProductServiceTest#testECPValid</td></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Requirements</span><td colspan="3">cmir3500_F01:  AdaugareProdus [Version : 1]<br /></td></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Keywords:</span></td><td colspan="3">&nbsp;None<br/></td></tr>
</table>
</div>
<a name="toc_tc29153"></a><p>&nbsp;</p><div> <table class="tc" width="90%" ><tr><th colspan="4">Test Case P232-18: AddProduct_ECP_Invalid&nbsp;<span style="font-size: 80%;">[Version  : 1]</span></th></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Author:</span></td><td colspan="3">cmir3500</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan="4"><span class="label">Summary:</span><br /><p>Testarea adaugarii unui produs cu o valoare dintr-o clasa de echivalenta invalida (pret negativ). Se introduc datele: id=1, nume=&quot;cola&quot;, pret=-5. Rezultatul asteptat este ca sistemul sa respinga actiunea si sa arunce ValidationException.</p>
</td></tr><tr><td colspan="4"><span class="label">Preconditions:</span><br /><p>Aplicatia este pornita si initializata.</p>
</td></tr><tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Execution type:</span></td><td colspan="3">Automated</td></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Estimated exec. duration (min):</span></td><td colspan="3"></td></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Importance:</span></td><td colspan="3">Medium</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan="4"></td></tr><tr><td > name of the autotest class:</td><td  colspan = "3" >drinkshop.tests.ProductServiceTest</td></tr>
<tr><td > name of the test method:</td><td  colspan = "3" >drinkshop.tests.ProductServiceTest#testECPInvalidPret</td></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Requirements</span><td colspan="3">cmir3500_F01:  AdaugareProdus [Version : 1]<br /></td></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Keywords:</span></td><td colspan="3">&nbsp;None<br/></td></tr>
</table>
</div>
<a name="toc_tc29155"></a><p>&nbsp;</p><div> <table class="tc" width="90%" ><tr><th colspan="4">Test Case P232-19: AddProduct_BVA_Valid&nbsp;<span style="font-size: 80%;">[Version  : 1]</span></th></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Author:</span></td><td colspan="3">cmir3500</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan="4"><span class="label">Summary:</span><br /><p>Testarea adaugarii unui produs folosind exact valoarea de frontiera minima acceptata pentru pret. Se introduc datele: id=1, nume=&quot;cola&quot;, pret=1. Rezultatul asteptat este ca produsul sa fie salvat cu succes, fara erori.</p>
</td></tr><tr><td colspan="4"><span class="label">Preconditions:</span><br /><p>Aplicatia este pornita si initializata. Nu exista deja un produs salvat cu id-ul 1.</p>
</td></tr><tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Execution type:</span></td><td colspan="3">Automated</td></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Estimated exec. duration (min):</span></td><td colspan="3"></td></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Importance:</span></td><td colspan="3">Medium</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan="4"></td></tr><tr><td > name of the autotest class:</td><td  colspan = "3" >drinkshop.tests.ProductServiceTest</td></tr>
<tr><td > name of the test method:</td><td  colspan = "3" >drinkshop.tests.ProductServiceTest#testBVAValidOne</td></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Requirements</span><td colspan="3">cmir3500_F01:  AdaugareProdus [Version : 1]<br /></td></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Keywords:</span></td><td colspan="3">&nbsp;None<br/></td></tr>
</table>
</div>
<a name="toc_tc29157"></a><p>&nbsp;</p><div> <table class="tc" width="90%" ><tr><th colspan="4">Test Case P232-20: AddProduct_BVA_Invalid&nbsp;<span style="font-size: 80%;">[Version  : 1]</span></th></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Author:</span></td><td colspan="3">cmir3500</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan="4"><span class="label">Summary:</span><br /><p>Testarea reactiei sistemului la o valoare fix sub limita inferioara acceptata pentru pret. Se introduc datele: id=1, nume=&quot;cola&quot;, pret=0. Rezultatul asteptat este ca sistemul sa arunce ValidationException si produsul sa nu fie salvat.</p>
</td></tr><tr><td colspan="4"><span class="label">Preconditions:</span><br /><p>Aplicatia este pornita si initializata.</p>
</td></tr><tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Execution type:</span></td><td colspan="3">Automated</td></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Estimated exec. duration (min):</span></td><td colspan="3"></td></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Importance:</span></td><td colspan="3">Medium</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan="4"></td></tr><tr><td > name of the autotest class:</td><td  colspan = "3" >drinkshop.tests.ProductServiceTest</td></tr>
<tr><td > name of the test method:</td><td  colspan = "3" >drinkshop.tests.ProductServiceTest#testBVAInvalidZero</td></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Requirements</span><td colspan="3">cmir3500_F01:  AdaugareProdus [Version : 1]<br /></td></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Keywords:</span></td><td colspan="3">&nbsp;None<br/></td></tr>
